k due to\nthe formation of long Fe nanowires inside the tubes, which might introduce an\nalignment in the random structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Aug 2011 16:02:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-29"}
