 consistent at the 3 sigma\nlevel to that evaluated from the UVES data using the line fitting procedure.\nThis reflects the low saturation of the detected GRB 081008 absorption\nfeatures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Aug 2011 11:20:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-08-05"}
